Today, our military leaders testified they recommended to Biden to leave troops in Afghanistan—a rec clearly rejected. 

@SecDef also told me the admin didn’t plan for an immediate collapse of the Afghan govt.

Biden’s decision to withdraw on a date certain boxed our military in. https://t.co/YMfvFc600M

